---
title: Mexican-Style Tofu & Charred Corn Tacos with Smokey Aioli
description: Get ready to spice up your tofu tonight. We reckon it's the key to a tasty taco. Well, that and the little kernels of juicy charred corn, slaw and the punchy smokey aioli. This dish is likely to get everyone on the tofu taco train!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-tofu-tacos-055550f9.jpg
